on (confidence man)">William Thompson</a> · <a href="/wiki/Joseph_Weil" title="Joseph Weil">Joseph Weil</a> · <a href="/wiki/Category:Fictional_con_artists" title="Category:Fictional con artists">Fictional con artists</a></div>
